    <item>
      <title>布雷纳德谈通货膨胀、红海危机和美国钢铁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-22/brainard-on-inflation-red-sea-crisis-and-us-steel-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫国家经济委员会主任莱尔·布雷纳德表示，现在还不是宣布通胀胜利的时候。布雷纳德在彭博电视台发表讲话时还就红海航运危机和新日铁拟收购美国钢铁公司发表了评论。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-22/brainard-on-inflation-red-sea-crisis-and-us-steel-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 17:25:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国债券创三月以来最佳表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/us-bonds-are-on-best-run-since-march-as-extreme-rate-bets-grow</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债将连续第四周上涨——自三月份以来的最佳连胜纪录——建立投资者对美联储下季度开始降息的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/us-bonds-are-on-best-run-since-march-as-extreme-rate-bets-grow</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 17:19:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西国家石油公司正在与穆巴达拉就巴伊亚炼油厂的股份进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/petrobras-in-talks-with-mubadala-for-stake-in-bahia-refinery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西国家石油公司巴西国家石油公司表示，它正在与穆巴达拉资本进行谈判，以回购其两年前出售给阿布扎比主权财富基金投资部门的一家炼油厂的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/petrobras-in-talks-with-mubadala-for-stake-in-bahia-refinery</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 17:17:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于数据推动降息押注，美元跌至七月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/euro-hits-strongest-since-august-as-dollar-eases-on-us-rate-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储首选的潜在通胀指标显示物价上涨温和后，美元延续跌势，证实了央行明年转向降息的立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-22/euro-hits-strongest-since-august-as-dollar-eases-on-us-rate-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Dec 2023 10:39:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股市迎来多年来最长的每周上涨：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在通胀数据增强了华尔街明年提前大幅降息的信念后，美国股市仍有望迎来为期八周的牛市。美国国债也准备每周上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
